      "content": "i mean i know, but people dont really help. it just feels like everyone is just pretending that anything matters so they dont have to face the reality of it. like we're all just biological accidents stumbling around in the dark. it's hard to see the point in talking to someone else when we're all just heading toward the same inevitable nothingness anyway.",
